"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Iran has been attacking Gulf states, and a person in Dubai was killed by falling debris. Iran says it has the right to defend itself if the UK joins US-Israeli attacks.\",            \"english_title\": \"Iran and Gulf Tensions\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ir\u00e1n ha estado atacando a los estados del Golfo, y una persona en Dub\u00e1i muri\u00f3 por escombros que cayeron. Ir\u00e1n dice que tiene derecho a defenderse si el Reino Unido se une a los ataques de EE.UU. e Israel.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tensiones entre Ir\u00e1n y el Golfo\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"An Israeli operation resulted in at least 41 deaths and 40 injuries, according to Lebanon's health ministry.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israeli Operation Casualties\",            \"translated_version\": \"Una operaci\u00f3n israel\u00ed caus\u00f3 al menos 41 muertes y 40 heridos, seg\u00fan el ministerio de salud de L\u00edbano.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Muertes en Operaci\u00f3n Israel\u00ed\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Ukraine is using armed robots in its fight against Russian forces. Ukraine's President Zelensky says people, including children, are injured as rescuers search through rubble.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ukraine Uses Armed Robots\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ucrania est\u00e1 usando robots armados en su lucha contra las fuerzas rusas. El presidente de Ucrania, Zelensky, dice que personas, incluidos ni\u00f1os, est\u00e1n heridos mientras los rescatistas buscan entre los escombros.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ucrania Usa Robots Armados\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Flights at Nairobi Airport are disrupted, and some roads in the capital are flooded.\",            \"english_title\": \"Nairobi Airport Disruptions\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los vuelos en el aeropuerto de Nairobi est\u00e1n interrumpidos, y algunas calles en la capital est\u00e1n inundadas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Problemas en Aeropuerto de Nairobi\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"US President Donald Trump plans to meet with Latin American leaders to counter China's influence in the region.\",            \"english_title\": \"Trump's Meeting with Latin Leaders\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU., Donald Trump, planea reunirse con l\u00edderes de Am\u00e9rica Latina para contrarrestar la influencia de China en la regi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Reuni\u00f3n de Trump con L\u00edderes Latinos\"        }    ]}"